 SVMrejected option is chosen. Default: False.\nThreshold_rej : Threshold used when rejecting the cells, default is 0.7.\nmeta_atlas : If the flag is added the predictions will use meta_atlas data.\nThis means that reference_H5AD and LabelsPath do not need to be specified."]}, {"name": "cPredictor.SVM_prediction.SVM_import", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "query_H5AD", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "OutputDir", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "SVM_type", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "replicates", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "sub_rep", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "colord", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "meta_atlas", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "show_bar", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "show_median", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Imports the output of the SVM_predictor and saves it to the query_H5AD.\n\nParameters:\nquery_H5AD: H5AD file of datasets of interest.\nOutputDir: Output directory defining the path of the exported SVM_predictions.\nSVM_type: Type of SVM prediction, SVM (default) or SVMrej.\nReplicates: A string value specifying a column in query_H5AD.obs.\ncolord: A .tsv file with the order of the meta_atlas and corresponding colors.\nmeta_atlas : If the flag is added the predictions will use meta_atlas data.\nshow_bar: Shows bar plots depending on the SVM_type, split over replicates.\nsub_rep:  A string value specifying an instance within the selected column in query_H5AD.obs.\nshow_median: Shows the median values of the distribution of the predictions."]}, {"name": "cPredictor.SVM_prediction.SVM_performance", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "reference_H5AD", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "LabelsPath", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "OutputDir", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "rejected", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "Threshold_rej", "type": null, "default":